import i18n from "i18next";
import { initReactI18next } from "react-i18next";

i18n.use(initReactI18next).init({
  resources: {
    en: {
      translation: {
        welcome: "Welcome to NFT Equipment Market",
        login_with_metamask: "Login with MetaMask",

        list_for_rent: "List for Rent",

        list_success: "Item listed successfully",
        list_error_missing_fields: "Please fill in all required fields",
        list_failed: "Listing failed: {{message}}",

        for_sale: "For Sale",
        for_rent: "For Rent",
        days: "days",
        buy: "Buy",
        price: "Price",
        confirm_buy: "Confirm Buy",
        buy_success: "Purchase successful",
        buy_failed: "Purchase failed: {{message}}",
        rent: "Rent",
        daily_rent: "Daily Rent",
        rental_days: "Rental Days",
        total_rent: "Total Rent",
        confirm_rent: "Confirm Rent",
        rent_success: "Rental successful",
        rent_failed: "Rental failed: {{message}}",
        back: "Back",
        cancel: "Cancel",
        attribute_labels: [
          "Attack Power",
          "Ability Power",
          "Armor Penetration",
          "Life Steal",
          "Attack Speed",
          "Health Points",
          "Armor",
          "Magic Resist",
          "Mana",
          "Mana Regeneration",
          "Movement Speed",
          "Healing & Shielding",
        ],
        attribute_names: {
          attackPower: "Attack Power",
          abilityPower: "Ability Power",
          armorPenetration: "Armor Penetration",
          lifeSteal: "Life Steal",
          attackSpeed: "Attack Speed",
          healthPoints: "Health Points",
          armor: "Armor",
          magicResist: "Magic Resist",
          mana: "Mana",
          manaRegeneration: "Mana Regeneration",
          movementSpeed: "Movement Speed",
          healingShielding: "Healing & Shielding",
        },
        equipment_types: [
          { id: 0, name: "Weapon", icon: "/images/weapon.png" },
          { id: 1, name: "Upper Body", icon: "/images/upperBody.png" },
          { id: 2, name: "Pants", icon: "/images/pants.png" },
          { id: 3, name: "Shoes", icon: "/images/shoes.png" },
          { id: 4, name: "Helmet", icon: "/images/helmet.png" },
        ],
      },
    },
    zh: {
      translation: {
        welcome: "欢迎使用 NFT 装备市场",
        login_with_metamask: "使用 MetaMask 登录",

        enter_equipment_name: "输入装备名称",

        mint: "铸造",
        mint_success: "铸造成功",
        mint_error_missing_data: "缺少合约或装备名称",
        mint_failed: "铸造失败: {{message}}",
        unlisted_items: "未上架物品",
        listed_items: "已上架物品",
        type: "类型",
        list: "上架",

        list_for_rent: "出租",

        delist_failed: "下架失败: {{message}}",
        filter_attributes: "筛选属性",
        switch_to_list: "切换到列表视图",
        switch_to_preview: "切换到预览视图",
        for_sale: "出售",
        for_rent: "出租",
        days: "天",
        buy: "购买",
        price: "价格",
        confirm_buy: "确认购买",
        buy_success: "购买成功",
        buy_failed: "购买失败: {{message}}",
        rent: "租赁",

        confirm_rent: "确认租赁",
        rent_success: "租赁成功",
        rent_failed: "租赁失败: {{message}}",

        cancel: "取消",
        attribute_labels: [
          "攻击力",
          "法术强度",
          "穿甲",
          "吸血",
          "攻击速度",
          "生命值",
          "护甲",
          "魔抗",
          "法力值",
          "法力回复速度",
          "移动速度",
          "回复与护盾强度",

        attribute_names: {
          attackPower: "攻击力",
          abilityPower: "法术强度",
          armorPenetration: "穿甲",
          lifeSteal: "吸血",
          attackSpeed: "攻击速度",
          healthPoints: "生命值",
          armor: "护甲",
          magicResist: "魔抗",
          mana: "法力值",
          manaRegeneration: "法力回复速度",
          movementSpeed: "移动速度",
          healingShielding: "回复与护盾强度",
        },
        equipment_types: [
          { id: 0, name: "武器", icon: "/images/weapon.png" },
          { id: 1, name: "上衣", icon: "/images/upperBody.png" },
          { id: 2, name: "裤子", icon: "/images/pants.png" },
          { id: 3, name: "鞋子", icon: "/images/shoes.png" },
          { id: 4, name: "头盔", icon: "/images/helmet.png" },
        ],
      },
    },
  },
  lng: "en",
  fallbackLng: "en",
  interpolation: { escapeValue: false },
